00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:53.839
Now, I'm a decrepit old man.

00:05:55.560 --> 00:05:58.399
I no longer have any desires.

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:00.639
I'm just

00:06:01.639 --> 00:06:02.639
counting my days here.

00:06:07.879 --> 00:06:08.560
Sir,

00:06:08.620 --> 00:06:10.519
as per the rules,
the first thing we should do

00:06:10.519 --> 00:06:13.480
is to take our guests
to your collection gallery.

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:17.000
Indeed. Elder Yu, your collection gallery
is renowned throughout the world.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.639
It's been so long
since we had visited the place.

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:20.920
