00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:30.639
to the collection gallery.

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:31.600
Yes, sir.

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:33.920
Everyone, please follow me.

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:35.680
Scrappy.

00:06:35.959 --> 00:06:36.959
(Scrappy)
Serve our master well.

00:06:37.199 --> 00:06:37.680
Yes, ma'am.

00:06:38.079 --> 00:06:38.639
Please.

00:06:57.399 --> 00:06:59.199
I heard that Elder Yu
was upright and honest.

00:06:59.720 --> 00:07:01.879
But now, there are
plenty of security guards here.

00:07:02.060 --> 00:07:03.790
This doesn't seem like
something he'll do.

00:07:04.330 --> 00:07:06.360
Elder Yu's lifetime collection
is all stored here.

00:07:06.600 --> 00:07:08.120
It can be considered a museum.

00:07:08.279 --> 00:07:09.120
Naturally,

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:10.560
we require more security guards here.

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:14.319
All of you may leave.

00:07:14.319 --> 00:07:14.990
- Yes, ma'am.
- Yes, ma'am.

00:07:20.839 --> 00:07:21.839
What is this?

00:07:23.580 --> 00:07:25.519
This is the
Coiled Dragon Bronze Tripod Cauldron.

00:07:25.650 --> 00:07:27.690
It's something
he's collected over half a lifetime.

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:29.720
He only brought it out in recent years.

00:07:30.839 --> 00:07:32.600
Miss Ning, you're truly an expert.

00:07:33.920 --> 00:07:35.270
Although you're new to the place,

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:37.439
you know about Elder Yu's collection

00:07:37.439 --> 00:07:38.520
like the back of your hand.

00:07:39.959 --> 00:07:43.399
I never expected such a treasure
to appear in a private collection.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:45.160
We're so lucky.

00:07:45.500 --> 00:07:47.000
My horizons have truly been broadened.

00:07:48.040 --> 00:07:50.199
Please feel free to explore on your own.

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:08.279
Grand in spirit,

00:08:09.040 --> 00:08:11.040
with forceful and vigorous strokes.

00:08:11.879 --> 00:08:13.150
The suspended-needle verticals

00:08:13.519 --> 00:08:14.759
fall like sharpened blades,

00:08:15.720 --> 00:08:17.160
the power piercing through the paper.

00:08:18.519 --> 00:08:19.879
Within inches of space,

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:22.040
I can see flashes of steel and
clashing swords.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:23.519
Excellent.

00:08:23.520 --> 00:08:25.450
Speaking of flashes of steel
and clashing swords,

00:08:25.460 --> 00:08:27.639
Brother, why do you not like
the Slender Gold script?

00:08:28.300 --> 00:08:30.470
At the turning points,
the tip is alternately concealed

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:32.860
and revealed, the movement
flows with controlled pauses and presses.

00:08:32.879 --> 00:08:34.759
Though extremely slender,
the strokes do not lose their substance,

00:08:34.760 --> 00:08:36.350
and thus possess a beauty of their own.

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:37.679
Regrettably, Huizong's weakness

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:39.000
led the nation astray.

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:40.180
He lacked true capability.

00:08:40.879 --> 00:08:42.240
His force is ultimately empty.

00:08:42.370 --> 00:08:43.720
He's not worth any serious regard.

