to buy a piece of land

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:21.200
to start a woman's swimming class.

00:09:22.420 --> 00:09:24.790
In the end, I was the one
who borrowed money on your behalf.

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:27.799
You take all of the credit.

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:31.679
But when there are hardships to endure,
you'll make sure I get half of them.

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:34.039
What do you know?

00:09:35.500 --> 00:09:36.890
You'd better mind your own business.

00:09:43.480 --> 00:09:44.240
Miss Wu,

00:09:44.799 --> 00:09:47.279
I don't think we've seen this before.

00:09:47.559 --> 00:09:48.159
Yeah.

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:51.200
There weren't this many exhibits
the last time we came here.

00:09:51.320 --> 00:09:52.240
We can always see

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:54.480
interesting items
whenever we visit here.

00:09:54.879 --> 00:09:55.559
This is great.

00:09:56.879 --> 00:09:59.000
Last time we came,
you didn't know a single thing.

00:09:59.039 --> 00:10:01.520
I've been catching up on work
for the past few years, you know?

00:10:05.679 --> 00:10:07.879
I'm truly honored
that you guys are here to visit me

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:10.159
during Double Ninth Festival.

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:11.840
Admiring autumn chrysanthemums,

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:13.080
wearing sprigs of dogwood,

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:14.360
savoring fine delicacies,

00:10:14.519 --> 00:10:15.559
and sipping fragrant tea.

00:10:15.840 --> 00:10:17.879
All of these are crucial.

00:10:19.879 --> 00:10:21.600
This chrysanthemum liquor smells great.

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:23.990
It's brewed by the local winery
below the mountains.

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:25.039
I thought

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:26.519
you brewed it yourself.

00:10:29.020 --> 00:10:31.500
Wearing sprigs of dogwood
during Double Ninth Festival, huh?

00:10:31.759 --> 00:10:33.000
This is quite interesting.

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:35.000
What's your name?

00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:36.480
My name is Chongyang.

00:10:36.679 --> 00:10:37.519
But,

00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:39.399
they call me Scrappy.

00:10:39.679 --> 00:10:41.120
Scrappy?

00:10:41.190 --> 00:10:42.519
Is it because you're mischievous?

00:10:43.759 --> 00:10:44.639
Scrappy,

00:10:45.159 --> 00:10:47.879
head to the room, bring out
the gifts that they brought for Master,

00:10:47.879 --> 00:10:48.919
and show them to him.

00:10:53.519 --> 00:10:54.320
Thank you, Elder Yu.

00:10:54.500 --> 00:10:56.700
Thank you for allowing us
to gather at this very place.

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:58.200
Let's offer Elder Yu a toast.

00:10:58.480 --> 00:10:59.240
Elder Yu,

00:10:59.240 --> 00:11:01.600
I wish you eternal happiness
and longevity!

00:11:02.330 --> 00:11:04.840
- Happy Double Ninth Festival.
- Happy Double Ninth Festival.

00:11:05.039 --> 00:11:05.879
Thank you.

00:11:05.879 --> 00:11:06.960
Likewise.

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:16.559
I know nothing else.

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:18.360
Let me sing a song for Godfather.

00:11:18.420 --> 00:11:20.400
Allow me to entertain you all
with a song of mine.

00:11:20.600 --> 00:11:21.679
Sure.

